\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 The Battle Mind}{\fs20\cf0  and }{\b\fs20\cf0 Telepath}{\fs20\cf0  advanced classes may take any metapsionic feat as a bonus feat, in addition to the bonus feats listed for those classes.
